# Restrict access to admin interface
# This adds an extra layer of security (though GitHub auth is the main protection)

# Only allow access from specific IPs (optional - uncomment and add your IPs)
# <RequireAll>
#   Require ip 192.168.1.0/24
#   Require ip YOUR_OFFICE_IP
# </RequireAll>

# Add security headers
Header always set X-Content-Type-Options nosniff
Header always set X-Frame-Options DENY
Header always set X-XSS-Protection "1; mode=block"
